# Contact form (Web3Forms) — free, sends submissions straight to your inbox.
# 1. Go to https://web3forms.com, enter the email where you want to receive messages.
# 2. Copy the Access Key they email you.
# 3. Create a file named `.env.local` next to this one and paste:
#    NEXT_PUBLIC_WEB3FORMS_KEY=your-access-key-here
# 4. Restart `npm run dev`.
# On Vercel, add the same variable under Project Settings → Environment Variables.
NEXT_PUBLIC_WEB3FORMS_KEY=
